---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: 首页
---
<section class="hero hero--garden"><div class="avatar" aria-hidden="true">晨</div><div class="hero__content"><p class="eyebrow">你好，我是</p><h1>晨汐</h1><p class="lede">{{ site.description }}</p></div></section>
<section class="garden-entries" aria-labelledby="garden-entries-title"><div class="section-heading"><p class="eyebrow">知识花园入口</p><h2 id="garden-entries-title">从一颗种子开始</h2></div><div class="garden-entries__grid"><a class="garden-entry garden-entry--cells" href="{{ '/细胞/' | url }}"><span class="garden-entry__icon" aria-hidden="true">🌱</span><span class="garden-entry__body"><strong>细胞</strong><span>从最小概念开始，把术语看懂</span></span></a><a class="garden-entry garden-entry--organs" href="{{ '/器官/' | url }}"><span class="garden-entry__icon" aria-hidden="true">🫀</span><span class="garden-entry__body"><strong>器官</strong><span>按用途学习，五大分类</span></span></a><a class="garden-entry garden-entry--individuals" href="{{ '/个体/' | url }}"><span class="garden-entry__icon" aria-hidden="true">🌿</span><span class="garden-entry__body"><strong>个体</strong><span>完整项目，从零到一</span></span></a><a class="garden-entry garden-entry--wiki" href="{{ '/组织wiki/' | url }}"><span class="garden-entry__icon" aria-hidden="true">📖</span><span class="garden-entry__body"><strong>组织 wiki</strong><span>术语词典，自动链接</span></span></a></div></section>
<section class="recent-posts" aria-labelledby="recent-posts-title"><div class="section-heading"><p class="eyebrow">持续生长中</p><h2 id="recent-posts-title">最近更新</h2></div><div class="cards">{% for post in collections.recent %}<a class="card" href="{{ post.url | url }}"><p class="eyebrow">{{ post.date | displayDate }}</p><h3>{{ post.data.title }}</h3><p>{{ post.data.description }}</p></a>{% endfor %}</div></section>
